
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>고급 생명과학 전지전능 암기봇</title>
    <style>
        :root { --primary: #6366f1; --bg: #0f172a; --card: #1e293b; --text: #f8fafc; --accent: #22d3ee; }
        body { font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif; background-color: var(--bg); color: var(--text); margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; min-height: 100vh; }
        #app { width: 95%; max-width: 900px; margin: 40px 0; }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .chapter-select { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        button { padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; border: none; background: var(--card); color: white; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; transition: 0.2s; }
        button:hover { background: #334155; }
        button.active { background: var(--primary); box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--primary); }
        .quiz-container { background: var(--card); padding: 25px; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }
        .sentence { line-height: 2.2; font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 20px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border-radius: 10px; border-left: 4px solid var(--primary); }
        input[type="text"] { background: transparent; border: none; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent); color: var(--accent); font-size: 1.1rem; text-align: center; outline: none; width: 120px; margin: 0 4px; }
        input.correct { border-bottom-color: #4ade80; color: #4ade80; }
        input.wrong { border-bottom-color: #f87171; color: #f87171; }
        .hint-area { height: 25px; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: center; font-weight: bold; }
        .controls { display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .status { text-align: right; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #64748b; margin-top: 15px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="app">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>🧬 고급 생명과학 완전 정복</h1>
        <p>모든 문장을 빈칸으로 만들었습니다. 화이팅!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="chapter-select">
        <button onclick="loadChapter(12)" id="btn12">12장. 세포주기</button>
        <button onclick="loadChapter(17)" id="btn17">17장. 유전자 발현</button>
        <button onclick="loadChapter(18)" id="btn18">18장. 발현 조절</button>
    </div>

    <div id="quiz-area" class="quiz-container" style="display:none;">
        <div id="hint-area" class="hint-area"></div>
        <div id="content"></div>
        <div class="controls">
            <button onclick="checkAnswers()" style="background: var(--accent); color: #000;">정답 확인</button>
            <button onclick="nextQuestion()">다음 문장 (셔플)</button>
            <button onclick="showAnswer()" style="background: #475569;">정답 보기</button>
        </div>
        <div id="status" class="status"></div>
    </div>
</div>

